short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A volume booster for modern browsers.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A volume booster for the media you love to watch and listen to. If your vacuum is too loud, problem solved! With this extension, you have the ability to increase the volume of any audio or video file by 500%. These settings save for each individual tab.
